CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 7, reads: "Attention State Liquor Control Board - How Many More Taverns Can Homewood-Brushton Stand? Within Two Blocks - In the 7500 and 7600 blocks of Tioga St., respectively, are... Di-Leo's Tavern (right photo).... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: 7600 block of Tioga Street with parked cars and Di-Leo's Tavern and grocery store, Homewood
